          <title>LeBron James has a triple-double and another win at Madison Square Garden as Lakers beat Knicks</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NEW YORK (AP) — LeBron James had 33 points, 12 assists and 11 rebounds in his 10th triple-double of the season, enjoying another memorable night at Madison Square Garden and leading the Los Angeles Lakers to a 128-112 victory over the New York Knicks on Saturday.]]></description>
