          <title>Despite Alex Ovechkin scoring his 877th goal, the Capitals lose to the Jets 5-4 in overtime</title>
          <description><![CDATA[WASHINGTON (AP) — Alex Ovechkin scored the 877th goal of his career to move 18 away from breaking the NHL record, but the Washington Capitals lost 5-4 in overtime to the Winnipeg Jets on Saturday night in a showdown of the top two teams in the NHL that lived up to that billing.]]></description>
